<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Leisurely" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Leisurely,</orth> adv. not in haste, deliberately, slowly: <cit><quote>promise more speed, but do it l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1349" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1349</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>where we may l. each one demand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.3.152" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 3, 152</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>so long agrowing and so l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.4.19" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 4, 19</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>